Jis Ka Jitna Ho Aanchal Yaha Par Usko Saugat Utni Milengi Jis Ka Jitna Ho Aanchal Yaha Par Usko Saugat Utni Milengi Phool Jivan Mein Gar Na Khile To Kaanto Se Bhi Nibhana Padenga Zindagi Pyar Ka Geet Hai Ise Har Dil Ko Gana Padenga.. Hai Agar Door Manzil To Kya Rasta Bhi Hai Mushkil To Kya Hai Agar Door Manzil To Kya Rasta Bhi Hai Mushkil To Kya Raat Taaron Bhari Na Mile To Dil Ka Deepak Ka Jalana Padenga Zindagi Pyar Ka Geet Hai Ise Har Dil Ko Gana Padenga.. Zindagi Ek Paheli Bhi Hai Sukh Dukh Ki Saheli Bhi Hai Zindagi Ek Paheli Bhi Hai Sukh Dukh Ki Saheli Bhi Hai Zindagi Ek Vachan Bhi To Hai Jise Sab Ko Nibhana Padenga
